data_frame.destination_panidentifier: uint16 (optional, present if Destination Addressing Mode is nonzero)
data_frame.destination_address: uint16 | uint64 (optional, present if Destination Addressing Mode is nonzero)
data_frame.source_panidentifier: uint16 (optional, present if Source Addressing Mode is nonzero and Intra-PAN is 0)
data_frame.source_address: uint16 | uint64 (optional, present if Source Addressing Mode is nonzero)

aps_ack_frame_header.extended header: variable (optional, present if Extended Header Present flag is set)
aps_ack_frame_header.destination endpoint: uint8 (present unless Ack Format is set)
aps_ack_frame_header.source endpoint: uint8 (present unless Ack Format is set)
aps_ack_frame_header.cluster identifier: uint16 (present unless Ack Format is set)
aps_ack_frame_header.profile identifier: uint16 (present unless Ack Format is set)
aps_ack_frame_header.block number: uint8 (optional, present if fragmentation is in use)
aps_ack_frame_header.ack bitfield: uint8 (optional, present if fragmentation is in use)

aps_data_frame_header.destination endpoint: uint8 (optional, present if Delivery Mode is 0b00 or 0b10)
aps_data_frame_header.group address: uint16 (optional, present if Delivery Mode is 0b11)
aps_data_frame_header.extended header: variable (optional, present if Extended Header Present flag is set)
